    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Deus Mantle</strong> 是一款基于进程的生存沙盒游戏，玩家将探索由程序生成的充满危险和神秘的无限世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为了完成神的旨意，你要准备好面对危险的生物，在这些艰难险阻中，你可能会找到回家的路。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116870/extras/c4bd7ed65541720b570d023b4b303ea7.webp?t=1767935603\" width=507 height=47 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个生物群落都有独特的材料可以收集，也有独特的挑战需要克服！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116870/extras/a8768dd7eab9d457c804beaead52e9db.poster.avif?t=1767935603\" width=540 height=296 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116870/extras/a8768dd7eab9d457c804beaead52e9db.webm?t=1767935603\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116870/extras/a8768dd7eab9d457c804beaead52e9db.mp4?t=1767935603\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在沙地沙漠寻找美味的辣椒，在雪地森林挖掘雪球，在深山老林迷失方向寻找珍贵的浆果。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116870/extras/338a875ebab11d0fedb6ec7b727deada.webp?t=1767935603\" width=569 height=47 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过科技树前进，解锁不同的物品、建筑和游戏机制。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116870/extras/9f3df6b31ae8c8e1193e614ad15d2700.poster.avif?t=1767935603\" width=540 height=296 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116870/extras/9f3df6b31ae8c8e1193e614ad15d2700.webm?t=1767935603\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116870/extras/9f3df6b31ae8c8e1193e614ad15d2700.mp4?t=1767935603\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 从零开始到建造魔法工厂来制造材料，这样你就可以给这些材料加魔法，从而更快地制造材料！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116870/extras/498741f44bfabb55afb094ecd528965d.webp?t=1767935603\" width=407 height=47 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用找到的所有材料，按照自己的意愿建造自己的基地。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116870/extras/36384c236835cd649df31af52189eb2a.poster.avif?t=1767935603\" width=540 height=296 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116870/extras/36384c236835cd649df31af52189eb2a.webm?t=1767935603\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116870/extras/36384c236835cd649df31af52189eb2a.mp4?t=1767935603\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用家具装饰你的家，用自动化优化你的材料生产方式，别忘了浇灌你的庄稼！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116870/extras/f11aa7d25d8dc96a585c9680ecc814d4.webp?t=1767935603\" width=436 height=46 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用你建造的装备砍杀敌人，或用元素魔法连击敌人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116870/extras/9376534ab0d4098adb64d478e4d5a907.poster.avif?t=1767935603\" width=540 height=296 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116870/extras/9376534ab0d4098adb64d478e4d5a907.webm?t=1767935603\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116870/extras/9376534ab0d4098adb64d478e4d5a907.mp4?t=1767935603\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >准备好挑战高难度的 Boss，获得独一无二的奖励。</p>",
